parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the Passlock anti-theft system can cause the vehicle to not start, leaving the driver stranded, which can lead to accidents or other safety risks.
symptoms: The vehicle will not start
the Passlock icon on the dashboard flashes
and the vehicle may crank but not fire.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition switch can cause the vehicle to not start, leaving the driver stranded, which can lead to accidents or other safety risks.
symptoms: The vehicle will not start
the ignition switch feels loose or worn out
and the vehicle may crank but not fire.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch hydraulic system can cause the clutch pedal to stick to the floor, making it difficult or impossible to shift gears, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
the clutch pedal does not return to its normal position
and the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ABS brake system can cause the brakes to malfunction, leading to accidents or loss of control, which can result in serious injury or death.
symptoms: The ABS fault light illuminates
the brakes grab or pulsate
the brakes make a grinding or squealing noise
the brakes fail to engage properly
the vehicle vibrates or shakes when braking.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The close proximity of the brake and accelerator pedals can cause the driver to accidentally press both pedals simultaneously, leading to loss of control or accidents.
symptoms: The driver's foot accidentally presses both the brake and accelerator pedals
causing the vehicle to accelerate or decelerate unexpectedly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure to properly repair or replace the brake switch can cause the brakes to malfunction, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The brake switch recall was not properly addressed
leading to ongoing brake problems.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake light switch can cause the brake lights to malfunction, leading to accidents or near-misses, as other drivers may not be aware of the vehicle's intention to stop.
symptoms: Brake lights do not illuminate
brake lights remain illuminated while driving
cruise control system malfunctions
inability to shift out of park
brake pedal feels soft or spongy.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Inoperative brake lights can cause accidents or near-misses, as other drivers may not be aware of the vehicle's intention to stop.
symptoms: Brake lights do not illuminate
brake lights remain illuminated while driving
inability to shift out of park
brake pedal feels soft or spongy.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the cruise control system can cause accidents or near-misses, as the driver may lose control of the vehicle.
symptoms: Cruise control system malfunctions
inability to shift out of park
brake pedal feels soft or spongy.
